  "remarks": "Leader of the Mouvement pour l’Unification et le Jihad en Afrique de l’Ouest (MUJAO) (QDe.134). Has\nprovided logistical support to the Sahelian group Al Moulathamine, linked with the Organization of Al-Qaida in the Islamic Maghreb (QDe.014). International arrest warrant issued by Mauritania. Mother’s name is Tijal Bint Mohamed Dadda. Malian Passport no: A1447120, expired on 19 Oct. 2011. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 21 Feb. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed on: 22 Feb. 2013 (amended on 1 May 2019)",
